tened<br />\n\t2) slightly busy<br />\n\t3) slightly noisy<br />\n\t4) slightly higher<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHodge was occupied by all these thoughts, not to mention he was also thinking about the items on his agenda. On top of that, as he was behind the wheels, he had to watch out for traffic as well. It was not surprising that Hodge did not notice a particular figure amidst the crowd lined up outside the pizza shop. That particular figure was paying close attention to Hodge's car as it pulled out of the back alley. Pushing his cap down slightly, the figure made note of the time.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167888836209/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p788019/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p788019\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796603/\">小贝大儿子17岁的人生是这样的 看完我很受伤</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795700/\">每天都很累吗？做好3件小事让生活焕然一新</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796128/\">教学10年的老外告诉你：美国人最常的俚语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796585/\">真正说走就走的冒险：目的地未知，你来吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794753/\">6个月内你能学会的10项新技能</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796625/\">2016年iphone摄影赛获奖作品：一半来自中国</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794140/\">蜜桃臀羞羞呐！日本妈咪晒萌娃PP照萌翻网友<